    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这是一款怎样的卡牌游戏？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏是一款幻想题材的卡牌对战游戏，玩家需巧妙利用卡牌之间的联动技能，攻击对手并占领所有据点。卡牌在满足特定条件后可觉醒，获得更强大的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/10b162163cc5575259afb37e79b09c91.poster.avif?t=1732849203\" width=638 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/10b162163cc5575259afb37e79b09c91.webm?t=1732849203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/10b162163cc5575259afb37e79b09c91.mp4?t=1732849203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以利用特殊卡牌效果奇袭对手的主阵地，切断其补给线以赢得胜利，或是精心策划，逐一占领各个据点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/18e4c53ebbb3a8c2a4033b77141fb31b.poster.avif?t=1732849203\" width=800 height=526 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/18e4c53ebbb3a8c2a4033b77141fb31b.webm?t=1732849203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/18e4c53ebbb3a8c2a4033b77141fb31b.mp4?t=1732849203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一场对局的胜败，都取决于您作为指挥官的明智决策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 对局结束后，玩家可以利用获得的积分在商店中收集更多强大的卡牌，组建自己的强力牌组，挑战更具难度和趣味性的关卡。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/efe9da4d295728fd30ecf6c3ac36af2f.poster.avif?t=1732849203\" width=800 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/efe9da4d295728fd30ecf6c3ac36af2f.webm?t=1732849203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/efe9da4d295728fd30ecf6c3ac36af2f.mp4?t=1732849203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/d4bbb5662bfc9ca7a566129b12adb53f.poster.avif?t=1732849203\" width=800 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/d4bbb5662bfc9ca7a566129b12adb53f.webm?t=1732849203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253040/extras/d4bbb5662bfc9ca7a566129b12adb53f.mp4?t=1732849203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
